<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8'>
    <title>Code-Wars</title>
    <style>
      body{
        font-family: arial;
        margin: 0;
      }
      nav{
        background: #ff5353;
        padding: 20px 10px;
      }
      nav ul{
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0;
      }
      nav li{
        list-style-type: none;
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 0 10px 0 0;
      }
      nav a{
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 18px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px;
        display: block;
      }
      main, header{
        max-width: 960px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        padding: 0 10px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .problems ul{
        border: 1px solid black;
        background-color: #ffd5d5;
        margin-top: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }
      .problems a{
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .problems li{
        color: black;
        font-size: 18px;
        padding: 10px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <% if (user) { %>
        <li><a href='/logout'>Logout</a></li>
        <li><a href='/'>Homepage</a></li>
        <li><a href='/profile'>Profile</a></li>
        <% } else { %>
        <li><a href='/login'>Login</a></li>
        <% } %>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <% if (user) { %>
    <main>
      <h1>Codewars</h1>
      <h2>코딩 전쟁이 일어난다. 모든 대원들, 전투 준비!</h2>

      <img src='https://gitlab.com/vanilla-coding/bootcamp/backend/codewars/raw/master/codewars.png' width='956px' />

      <h2>원하는 문제를 클릭하세요! 당신의 도움이 필요합니다!</h2>

      <div class='problems'>
        <% for (let i = 0; i < problems.length; i++) { %>
          <ul>
            <a href='/problems/<%= problems[i].id %>'>
              <li>Title: <%= problems[i].title %></li>
              <li>Description: <%= problems[i].description %></li>
              <li>정답자: <%= problems[i].completed_users %>명</li>
              <li>난이도: Level <%= problems[i].difficulty_level %></li>
            </a>
          </ul>
        <% } %>
        </div>
    </main>
    <% } else { %>
    <header>
      <h1>You can use our services after Login.</h1>
      <h2>If you want to use our page Press the Button above.</h2>
      <img src='https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1459347268516-3ed71100e718?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=eyJhcHBfaWQiOjEyMDd9&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80' height='500px' />
    </header>
    <% } %>
  </body>
</html>
